      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-30/keir-starmer-s-future-as-prime-minister-faces-key-test-in-wales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当这位未来的总理试图制定适合现代世界的产业政策时，南威尔士将对他构成早期挑战。]]></description>
