    <item>
      <title>泰国总理斯雷塔支持率下滑，反对派势力不断壮大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/thai-pm-srettha-s-approval-rating-falls-as-opposition-s-popularity-keeps-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于法律和经济挑战不断增加，泰国总理斯雷塔·达维辛及其为泰党的支持率在最新民意调查中继续下降，而反对党的支持率则有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/thai-pm-srettha-s-approval-rating-falls-as-opposition-s-popularity-keeps-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 03:44:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚绿党推动成立原住民真相与正义机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/australia-s-greens-push-for-first-nations-truth-and-justice-body</link>
      <description><![CDATA[绿党本周将继续推动成立真相与正义委员会，调查澳大利亚土著人民遭受的不公正对待，并向联邦议会提交一份法案来成立该机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/australia-s-greens-push-for-first-nations-truth-and-justice-body</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 01:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克称工党将在数周内造成“不可逆转”的损害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-29/sunak-starmer-s-labour-would-inflict-irreversible-harm-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克警告称，基尔·斯塔默爵士可能在入主唐宁街 100 天内对英国造成“不可逆转的损害”，因为他挽救保守党选举希望的时间已经不多了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-29/sunak-starmer-s-labour-would-inflict-irreversible-harm-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 21:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在灾难性的辩论后要求捐助者继续支持他</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/biden-seeks-to-reassure-anxious-donors-at-nyc-region-fundraisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在纽约汉普顿向腰缠万贯的捐助者表示，他承认对自己与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论表现感到担忧，并发誓要坚持竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/biden-seeks-to-reassure-anxious-donors-at-nyc-region-fundraisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 16:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称工党领导的英国可以帮助民粹主义进步人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-warns-against-us-europe-populism-ahead-of-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，尽管欧洲和北美的右翼政党崛起，但工党领导的英国不会在全球舞台上陷入孤立，民意调查预测的英国下一任首相警告说，只有进步政党才能“应对”世界面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-warns-against-us-europe-populism-ahead-of-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 13:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长期支持者反对凯尔·斯塔默的工党，导致顶级球队明星面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/revolt-against-keir-starmer-s-labour-by-long-time-backers-puts-stars-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯明翰居民 Johur Uddin 一直投票支持工党。但随着英国反对党下周即将在选举中创下纪录，这位 56 岁的顾问表示，他将在 7 月 4 日打破一贯的习惯，在选票上独立候选人旁边画一个 X。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/revolt-against-keir-starmer-s-labour-by-long-time-backers-puts-stars-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
